Date   : 2020-10-19
o RELEASE 1.12
SIGNIFICANT USER-VISIBLE CHANGES
- New submission to CRAN after package was archived by CRAN on 2020-08-26 as CRAN 
  check issues were not corrected in time by its authors (at the time).
- Corrected and updated Import and Depends field values of DESCRIPTION file.
- Updated license version to GPL (>= 3), and added LICENSE file.
- Added new author and changed maintainer.
- Added GitHub repository for development and support.
- Hidden internal codes (functions never to be called by end-user).
- Added "inst" folder with documentation, CITATION and NEWS files.
- Added README file.
BUG FIXES
- Matched DESCRIPTION declarations and NAMESPACE directives.
- Corrected all R code problems to comply with R (>= 4.0.3).
- Removed deprecated Lazyload and LazyData field values of DESCRIPTION file.
- Cleaned up and formatted all LaTex codes of Rd manual files to comply with CRAN 
  checks.
- Added '\author{...}' and '\references{...}' fields in Rd manual files.
PACKAGE INSTALLATION
- Minor updates in manual files (Rd files).
- Minor updates in documentation files (DESCRIPTION and NEWS).
- Built and tested under R version 4.0.3 (2020-10-10).
- Migrated update to GitHub and tested by Travis CI.
